{"tid":2302764,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"回顧一下今年自己睇咗既戲","createTime":"2020-11-27T11:00:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T12:58:21.000Z","uid":124655,"like":5,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ea7e4a65a79da05674f493d0153bb59427c3b2dd","tid":2302764,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T11:00:06.000Z","msg":"今年年頭好多時開工不足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又唔出得街, <br />\n結果終於有時間睇咗好多好多戲, 今年睇既數目, 相等於過去幾年夾埋既數量<br />\n有啲係從來未睇過, 有啲係細個唔識欣賞, 大個咗先識睇既戲, 有啲係已經完全忘記, <br />\n翻睇當新睇既戲, 希望借過 Post 留一留痕, 下年再比較返, 大家今年有睇過咩戲, 不彷一齊貼吓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>Man of Steel - 超人&mdash;鋼鐵之軀 </strong></span><br />\n原本係睇 BVS, 但睇咗 10 分鐘, 發現有好多野提及返上集, 所以特登搵返上集黎睇先<br />\n<img src=\"https://pics.filmaffinity.com/Man_of_Steel-919390391-large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpics.filmaffinity.com%2FMan_of_Steel-919390391-large.jpg&h=4a10586e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice - 蝙蝠俠對超人：正義曙光 <br />\n</strong></span><br />\n反咗肥賓咁耐, 終於都有機會睇佢做既蝙蝠俠, 估唔到原來佢做中老年既蝙蝠俠又真係幾好睇<br />\n做到有個種英雄遲暮既感覺, 睇完之後都幾想睇佢做獨立一套既蝙蝠俠戲, 可惜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/2/20/Batman_v_Superman_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F2%2F20%2FBatman_v_Superman_poster.jpg&h=4d7546ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>Wonder Woman - 神奇女俠</strong></span><br />\n唔駛講啦, 睇 BVS 見到條女咁正, 邊有得唔睇埋佢套獨立電影  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> OK 好睇咁啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/f7/de/dc/f7dedc38e914bf78bb12608663afc879.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2Ff7%2Fde%2Fdc%2Ff7dedc38e914bf78bb12608663afc879.jpg&h=ac4d606d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>Justice League - 正義聯盟 </strong></span><br />\n跌咗落去, 唯有睇埋個正義聯盟, 我諗未必岩太多人睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係唔好睇, 可能只係唔岩我口味,<br />\n本身個人唔太鐘意睇大堆頭製作 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對面公司就更加小睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/91JNWWQKGgL._RI_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F91JNWWQKGgL._RI_.jpg&h=48356ce8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>Suicide Squad - 自殺突擊隊</strong></span><br />\n之後已經阻止唔到我繼續睇埋個系列佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都話咗唔鍾意睇大堆頭<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ruten.com.tw/s2/b/7f/10/21632297134864_701.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ruten.com.tw%2Fs2%2Fb%2F7f%2F10%2F21632297134864_701.jpg&h=a6df82a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>Batman Ninja (ニンジャバットマン, Ninja Battoman) </strong></span><br />\n最後, 痴到連 Batman 動畫都照睇埋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />未睇過既巴打, 我可以話你知呢套動畫絶對要睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />故事內容唔多提, 啲畫風正撚到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/89/af/66/89af66df6fd395c8381eeb9b60029eea.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F89%2Faf%2F66%2F89af66df6fd395c8381eeb9b60029eea.png&h=a5f11e15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYmFhYzZhYzgtZjZiYS00NWEwLWFhYTUtN2UxM2FmYzdhNDUyXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDk2Nzc1Mg@@._V1_UY1200_CR110,0,630,1200_AL_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.media-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FM%2FMV5BYmFhYzZhYzgtZjZiYS00NWEwLWFhYTUtN2UxM2FmYzdhNDUyXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDk2Nzc1Mg%40%40._V1_UY1200_CR110%2C0%2C630%2C1200_AL_.jpg&h=17c55772&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>The Bourne Identity - 叛諜追擊 1</strong></span><br />\n見睇完上面個系列悶悶地, 原本都唔想睇呢套, 因為一諗到麥迪文就會腦中出現一大蘿佢啲柒事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但悶起上黎唯有照睇住先......果然.....一部戲能夠有佢既系列, 確實係有佢既好睇之處,<br />\n部戲好睇之餘, 最正係啲配角可能會係下一集變成主角, 又有可能突然之間就會死撚咗, <br />\n<img src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BM2JkNGU0ZGMtZjVjNS00NjgyLWEyOWYtZmRmZGQyN2IxZjA2XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTIzOTk5ODM@._V1_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.media-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FM%2FMV5BM2JkNGU0ZGMtZjVjNS00NjgyLWEyOWYtZmRmZGQyN2IxZjA2XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTIzOTk5ODM%40._V1_.jpg&h=257fe5fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://therealzordon.files.wordpress.com/2014/10/bourneidentitynickyfilm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftherealzordon.files.wordpress.com%2F2014%2F10%2Fbourneidentitynickyfilm.jpg&h=c3b0e1e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>The Bourne Supremacy  - 叛諜追擊 2</strong></span><br />\n呢集開始既追逐畫面開始有港產片味道, 演員重越黎越正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/3/30/Bourne_supremacy_ver2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F3%2F30%2FBourne_supremacy_ver2.jpg&h=ea1bb06d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/1c/6e/8d/1c6e8d11f8ad6758d37e7716abf34d5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F1c%2F6e%2F8d%2F1c6e8d11f8ad6758d37e7716abf34d5b.jpg&h=55a9f87c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/07/0f/49/070f49f2936cd61c0d996f9c850ddc0a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F07%2F0f%2F49%2F070f49f2936cd61c0d996f9c850ddc0a.jpg&h=59349263&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://c8.alamy.com/comp/BNPXB5/joan-allen-julia-stiles-the-bourne-supremacy-2004-BNPXB5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc8.alamy.com%2Fcomp%2FBNPXB5%2Fjoan-allen-julia-stiles-the-bourne-supremacy-2004-BNPXB5.jpg&h=fd945579&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>The Bourne Ultimatum - 叛諜追擊 3</strong></span><br />\n呢集係公認既系列癲峰之作, 追逐畫面發生係祖國倫敦, 畫面除咗有大量英國風之外, <br />\n成個故既佈局同追逐, 跟踪, 完全係港產片既味道, 好撚正呀媽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.wallpaperup.com/uploads/wallpapers/2015/01/01/571052/aacf76520c07368f96e7489627cf4260-700.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wallpaperup.com%2Fuploads%2Fwallpapers%2F2015%2F01%2F01%2F571052%2Faacf76520c07368f96e7489627cf4260-700.jpg&h=4705aa12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.mi9.com/uploads/movie-tv/1474/julia-stiles-nicky-parsons-in-2007-the-bourne-ultimatum_1280x1024_20758.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.mi9.com%2Fuploads%2Fmovie-tv%2F1474%2Fjulia-stiles-nicky-parsons-in-2007-the-bourne-ultimatum_1280x1024_20758.jpg&h=7a17fcda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://southbanklondon.com/sites/default/files/2017-01/THE%20BOURNE%20ULTIMATUM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsouthbanklondon.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2017-01%2FTHE%2520BOURNE%2520ULTIMATUM.jpg&h=74208899&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <span class=\"large\"><strong>The Bourne Legacy - 叛諜追擊 4</strong></span><br />\n呢集眾所鳩知係外傳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 叫做好好醜醜睇埋佢, 都唔係話唔好睇既, 起碼女主角都幾 JJable <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但最尾個 Asset 好撚廢, 唔知佢出黎做乜鳩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, btw, 演員落力係真既, 有幾個鏡頭都睇到男主角親身上陣<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/6f/b6/1e/6fb61ecfaceb7d554c4ab150b70856f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F6f%2Fb6%2F1e%2F6fb61ecfaceb7d554c4ab150b70856f9.jpg&h=c2b67396&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/c5/16/0e/c5160e954788ca7d8537be15a25194c7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2Fc5%2F16%2F0e%2Fc5160e954788ca7d8537be15a25194c7.jpg&h=f70466d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.hypesphere.com/2012/07/jeremy-renner-the-bourne-legacy-movie-600x4001.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.hypesphere.com%2F2012%2F07%2Fjeremy-renner-the-bourne-legacy-movie-600x4001.jpeg&h=0885b0a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>Jason Bourne - 叛諜追擊 5</strong></span><br />\n終於睇到系列最尾一集, 感覺同 3 好相近, 但又冇 3 咁有內咸, 睇到中段我已經忍唔撚住大嗌<br />\n導演我屌你老母呀 !!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />封面條女同實機圖唔撚一樣既 <br />\n忍撚住唔劇透先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/a9/e8/bf/a9e8bfbdd5472aff7a1dfe0813795401.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2Fa9%2Fe8%2Fbf%2Fa9e8bfbdd5472aff7a1dfe0813795401.jpg&h=f4bcd019&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/1b/4a/83/1b4a83d0c4c010952b295be39b9ac580.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F1b%2F4a%2F83%2F1b4a83d0c4c010952b295be39b9ac580.jpg&h=8273fff1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/b8b0daa81294b6410fb15080a2b4ce64/tumblr_inline_p5y2vdf8HE1qlswdc_500.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F64.media.tumblr.com%2Fb8b0daa81294b6410fb15080a2b4ce64%2Ftumblr_inline_p5y2vdf8HE1qlswdc_500.jpg&h=e842ea7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黎到呢度我居然已經睇咗兩部戲既系列作, 已經覺得自己好勁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 亦見證咗我已經好多日冇工開......"},{"pid":"43f7da2b3741fbfbb1ee08f4ad6671086c76914d","tid":2302764,"uid":124655,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T11:00:40.000Z","msg":"睇完咗兩個系列之後, 就開始咗搵散戲睇, 順序大致如下<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>The Last Emperor - 末代皇帝溥儀</strong></span><br />\n因為覺得尊龍太靚仔, 所以忍唔住搵呢套戲黎睇, 呢部戲係戲院放既時候我<br />\n應該重係蛋白汁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.kfs.io/album/global/950727,0v1/fit/500x500.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.kfs.io%2Falbum%2Fglobal%2F950727%2C0v1%2Ffit%2F500x500.jpg&h=6bd15374&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.austinchronicle.com/binary/bd2b/SS.LastEmperor.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.austinchronicle.com%2Fbinary%2Fbd2b%2FSS.LastEmperor.jpg&h=9ad87365&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/30/012052_890686b624d68d37250041025ddfdd94.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F30%2F012052_890686b624d68d37250041025ddfdd94.jpg&h=c26f1ea7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>War Game - 戰爭遊戲</strong></span><br />\n呢部戲睇啲評論話當年列根睇完都得到好多啓發, 算係電腦保安既一個重要電影, <br />\n所以先搵黎睇, 好唔好睇就等有興趣既大家自己去睇去評 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好彩列根當年既對手唔係連登仔...<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/81sR8GwMDQL._RI_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F81sR8GwMDQL._RI_.jpg&h=186d74a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BN2E0YmYwMmQtOWU2YS00MDcxLThmMjctZWYxMzhkZmY0MTBhXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjAwODA4Mw@@._V1_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.media-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FM%2FMV5BN2E0YmYwMmQtOWU2YS00MDcxLThmMjctZWYxMzhkZmY0MTBhXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjAwODA4Mw%40%40._V1_.jpg&h=a09d684b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>1408</strong></span><br />\n呢部咁出名, 唔駛我講啦, 由部戲上畫前已經想睇, 到部戲落咗畫咁多年我先終於睇, <br />\n叫做完咗件事.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-glyOdE9fFnA/UH6w7dRLH0I/AAAAAAAAJEY/-uZEY2PTWPc/s1600/p887024663.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-glyOdE9fFnA%2FUH6w7dRLH0I%2FAAAAAAAAJEY%2F-uZEY2PTWPc%2Fs1600%2Fp887024663.jpg&h=e8f4bc40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/sgp-catalog-images/region_US/weinstein-TWC1021-Full-Image_GalleryBackground-en-US-1483993185333._RI_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FS%2Fsgp-catalog-images%2Fregion_US%2Fweinstein-TWC1021-Full-Image_GalleryBackground-en-US-1483993185333._RI_.jpg&h=a682d698&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>Get Out - 逃出絕命鎮</strong></span><br />\n呢部又係啦, 咁出名, 主要講 Nigga 食開條白滑鬼妹, 跟住同佢返去條女屋企探親探出事,<br />\n條女主睇落幾仁, 專食黑腸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Once you try black, you never back<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/a/a3/Get_Out_poster.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fa%2Fa3%2FGet_Out_poster.png&h=8f611882&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNDdkNDlmOTgtNmZkZC00MjVjLThmYzgtY2NmOWM5OTE3ZmY5XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTE4MDg3NTIz._V1_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.media-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FM%2FMV5BNDdkNDlmOTgtNmZkZC00MjVjLThmYzgtY2NmOWM5OTE3ZmY5XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTE4MDg3NTIz._V1_.jpg&h=a7dcc78d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.insider.com/58b9b45846017824008b4a7b?width=1200&amp;format=jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F58b9b45846017824008b4a7b%3Fwidth%3D1200%26format%3Djpeg&h=78cecfe1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>Alien - 異形4：浴火重生</strong></span><br />\n對呢集冇咩想講, 總結係好睇過第 3 集, even 第三集係名導演拍, 我都係覺得第 4 集好睇過第 3 集<br />\n<img src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNDljNGZkNmItNDlmMi00YzJhLWJiYWUtNGY4OGEwNmY0ODg4XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTAyODkwOQ@@._V1_UY1200_CR99,0,630,1200_AL_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.media-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FM%2FMV5BNDljNGZkNmItNDlmMi00YzJhLWJiYWUtNGY4OGEwNmY0ODg4XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTAyODkwOQ%40%40._V1_UY1200_CR99%2C0%2C630%2C1200_AL_.jpg&h=ef296fec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://bloody-disgusting.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Screen-Shot-2018-12-04-at-9.10.46-AM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbloody-disgusting.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2FScreen-Shot-2018-12-04-at-9.10.46-AM.png&h=67cfd03a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>Kick-Ass 2 踢屎忽 2</strong></span><br />\n唔駛講, 正常連登仔應該都係會有睇過, 好睇既會覺得好睇, 唔好睇既應該就唔會覺得好睇,<br />\n睇完好想操到男主角個身型出黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 非gay師<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/91CW1MAwSdL._SY445_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F91CW1MAwSdL._SY445_.jpg&h=b61d9dd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/39/81/1a/39811ad3a44e37695fe5212cefa8a532.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F39%2F81%2F1a%2F39811ad3a44e37695fe5212cefa8a532.jpg&h=e5b30884&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>The Hunt Of Red October - 追擊赤色十月</strong></span><br />\n經典潛艇電影, 今次係翻睇, 都唔係好記得啲劇情了, 睇完冇幾耐辛康納尼就走咗啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/3/36/The_Hunt_for_Red_October_movie_poster.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F3%2F36%2FThe_Hunt_for_Red_October_movie_poster.png&h=f8411624&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong> ARGO - 救參任務</strong></span><br />\n為咗睇賓而睇, 除咗開頭 10 分鐘同尾 10 分鐘外, 我覺得中段其實悶到我.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://oneyeasee.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Argo-ARGO%E2%80%93%E6%95%91%E5%8F%83%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99-%E4%BA%9E%E6%9E%9C%E5%87%BA%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99-400x650.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Foneyeasee.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2FArgo-ARGO%25E2%2580%2593%25E6%2595%2591%25E5%258F%2583%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%258B%2599-%25E4%25BA%259E%25E6%259E%259C%25E5%2587%25BA%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%258B%2599-400x650.jpg&h=4f19cb1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh-yue/8/82/Argo_2012_movie.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh-yue%2F8%2F82%2FArgo_2012_movie.jpg&h=3896f928&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>The Purge - 國定殺戮日</strong></span><br />\n暫時睇咗第一集, 冇我期望既咁好睇, 覺得大屠殺剌激好多囉<br />\n<img src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTQzNTcwODEyM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMjM1MDI0OQ@@._V1_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.media-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FM%2FMV5BMTQzNTcwODEyM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMjM1MDI0OQ%40%40._V1_.jpg&h=3c78a373&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images6.fanpop.com/image/photos/39700000/The-Purge-horror-movies-39737564-460-300.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages6.fanpop.com%2Fimage%2Fphotos%2F39700000%2FThe-Purge-horror-movies-39737564-460-300.jpg&h=129b19c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>Olympus Has Fallen - 全面攻佔 : 白官淪陷</strong></span><br />\n想睇北韓點樣入侵美國既一定要睇呢部 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大北韓主意, 寵寵寵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/51JrqEniwnL._SY445_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F51JrqEniwnL._SY445_.jpg&h=6960af94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.angryasianman.com/images/angry/olympushasfallen01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.angryasianman.com%2Fimages%2Fangry%2Folympushasfallen01.jpg&h=90bcebf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>London Has Fallen - 全面攻佔2：倫敦救援</strong></span><br />\n一句講晒, 如果想浪費人生既時間就可以睇吓, 講完.....<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/91Lk9v9rpnL._SL1500_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F91Lk9v9rpnL._SL1500_.jpg&h=6a786043&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BOTA2MDk3NTAwNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODMzMzk3NzE@._V1_CR0,60,640,360_AL_UX477_CR0,0,477,268_AL_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.media-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FM%2FMV5BOTA2MDk3NTAwNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODMzMzk3NzE%40._V1_CR0%2C60%2C640%2C360_AL_UX477_CR0%2C0%2C477%2C268_AL_.jpg&h=35fc92ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>E.T. - ET 外星人</strong></span><br />\n呢部呢兩日會睇埋佢, 作為 00 後, 未睇過呢部戲係冇乜咁出奇, 就等我今個禮拜睇埋佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/geekbase/157500521753.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fgeekbase%2F157500521753.jpg&h=e6752b05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>Tora, Tora, Tora - 偷襲珍珠港</strong></span><br />\n希望年尾前可以睇埋呢部, 覺得睇部戲需要既時間同心力應該不小 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Video3/v4/59/c7/23/59c72361-fa17-eda6-cdc7-7b47b61965c6/000018.jpg/268x0w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis1-ssl.mzstatic.com%2Fimage%2Fthumb%2FVideo3%2Fv4%2F59%2Fc7%2F23%2F59c72361-fa17-eda6-cdc7-7b47b61965c6%2F000018.jpg%2F268x0w.jpg&h=b4a07614&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c5841f2328ec87ee7e8b43f42c8c6e35c941298b","tid":2302764,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T11:02:56.000Z","msg":"暫時以 24 部戲作結, 輪到大家出招 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上面啲戲有咩想問可以即管問, 暫時都重記得啲劇情 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c285441aa7551976da9686f039bcfb593cb7d141","tid":2302764,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T11:11:02.000Z","msg":"最尾加小小圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.warhistoryonline.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Tora-Tora-Tora-1280x720.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.warhistoryonline.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F01%2FTora-Tora-Tora-1280x720.jpg&h=b21b4b80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.globalauctionplatform.com/feebf28c-c6c3-47f2-b679-a84f01034152/d9d947a4-47d7-43fc-a1af-c2b9ab023207/original.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=